everyday flow

worker:
- check unaccepted orders
- accept an order (or reject it)
- mark order as completed 

- change seat limit (or copy to next day)
- change products available  (or copy to next day)

manager:
(analytics?)
- get total spent for a company
- get product popularity
- get order amount per hour
- saved by discounts




consumer:
- list products and prices (with filtering)
- place an order
- update an order
- check order status
- make reservation

- check discount possibility
- check active discount
- activate discount